      "description": "Looking for an affordable project, parts car, or a budget ride to tinker with? This one has plenty of potential for someone who knows their way around cars and wants something they can put their own stamp on. It\u2019s not perfect, but it\u2019s an honest car being offered at a fair price, and for the right buyer it could be a really worthwhile pickup. If you want something cheap with possibilities, come take a look.",
